<p>3）单选框历史与使用<a href="https://www.zcool.com.cn/article/ZMTE0NzEwNA==.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zcool.com.cn/article/ZMTE0NzEwNA==.html</a></p>
<p>4）UI备忘单<a href="https://uxdesign.cc/ui-cheat-sheet-radio-buttons-checkboxes-and-other-selectors-bf56777ad59e" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://uxdesign.cc/ui-cheat-sheet-radio-buttons-checkboxes-and-other-selectors-bf56777ad59e</a></p>
<p>5）选择控件指南<a href="https://medium.com/tap-to-dismiss/select-to-proceed-996d19c8a7a4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.com/tap-to-dismiss/select-to-proceed-996d19c8a7a4</a></p>
